title: Fall Out Boy Discography (almost everything) part 2
description:
it's not really a 'part 2', but more of an update, everything that was in the last torrent, and more, including the new 'folie a deux'.

evening out with your girlfriend

take the to your grave (+bonus tracks)

from under the cork tree (+bonus tracks)

infinity on high (+'leaked in london' as part of bonus tracks)

fall out boy/project rocket split - only the fob tracks

live in phoenix

folie a deux (+bonus tracks/extra bonus tracks)

the welcome to the new administration mixtape - fob and many other bands (includes fob demos from folie a deux)

a few music videos are also thrown in (mp4)

+ b-sides, unreleased (more this time!), live, acoustics.

pretty much everything excluding radio edits etc.


if i have missed anything, you want something, you can request for it
